.cm SCRIPT REFERENCE EZ
.SUBT Purpose
The EasySCRIPT control word is used to initiate and provide
input to the EasySCRIPT macro processor.
.SUBT Format
×                <ON <lastDewey>>
×  .EZ           <OFF           >
×                <tagval line   >
.SUBT Usage
For now, refer to pages 60-65 and 92-93 of the
IBM SCRIPT/370 Version 3 User's Guide (SH20-1857) for
a description of the language and facilities.
.SUBT Notes
.of 4
(1) EasySCRIPT is currently in development and test.
It is not now distributed.
.in
.cm End of EZ
